name: testAddBuildStepsOptionsCollectToList
description: Verification of possibility to add build steps options for MultiConfiguration Project
descriptionHtml: Verification of possibility to add build steps options for MultiConfiguration Project

testStage.description: Verification of possibility to add build steps options for MultiConfiguration Project

steps.name: Click on 'New Item' in the side menu
Click 'Save' button on the BaseConfigPage page
Click 'Logo' button and move to main page
Click on the 'Configure' button on side menu
Click on the 'Configure' Button on the Base Job Page
Open build step options from dropdown menu
Get options in build step from dropdown menu
Logout from instance http://localhost:8081/
